Mine are close to that, but I was a bit lower on the silver stuff.
plus 2 silver, from 4plat to 6plat each
Jade rings 10plat
electrum jade on my server goes at a steady 20pp. Everyone just sticks
with that.
Also, WIS earings last night were a big seller. I sold about 20 of them,
at aroudn 8 to 10 pp each. They cost about 4 to make I think.
